ifN", "text_ar": "عَجِفٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A face having little flesh."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "livapN EajofaA='u", "text_ar": "لِثَةٌ عَجْفَا=ءُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A gum having little flesh."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$afataAni EajofaAwaAni", "text_ar": "شَفَتَانِ عَجْفَاوَانِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Two thin lips."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ks, O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "naSolN A^aEojafu", "text_ar": "نَصْلٌ اَعْجَفُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A thin,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "slender, arrow-head:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "niSaAlN EijaAfN", "text_ar": "نِصَالٌ عِجَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (O, K.) ―         -b3-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aroDN EajofaA='u", "text_ar": "اَرْضٌ عَجْفَا=ءُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Land in which is no good."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^araDuwna EijaAf", "text_ar": "اَرَضُونَ عِجَاف"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Lands not rained upon."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EijaAfN", "text_ar": "عِجَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is sometimes used [alone] as signifying"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Lands affected by drought:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a poet says, describing clouds ("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saHaAb", "text_ar": "سَحَاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "),"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "laqiHa AlEijaAfu lahu lisaAbiEi saboEapK"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The lands affected by drought produced herbage by reason thereof at a period of seven days"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "after the rain. (L, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["O", "K", "Msb", "TA", "S"]}]}, "classical_definit